snippet.title: Outdoors Inn
snippet.description:
A young-ish couple, their dog, and their loyal steed Good Time Charlie (a 2022 Globetrotter) welcome you to the Outdoors Inn. 

An Inn where the outdoors meets you and the festivities around greet you. Join us as we take our time traveling around to do ordinary stuff in extraordinary places and hearing the stories of the people who call them home. 

Y'all come back now,

Jameson, Devan, Dublin the Dog
